Ops Manager is a web application that you use to deploy and manage a [Pivotal Cloud Foundry](https://network.pivotal.io/products/pivotal-cf) (PCF) PaaS.
This is a guide to deploying and using Ops Manager.

## <a id='ops-man-ui'></a> Ops Manager UI

Use the Ops Manager UI to configure settings for your Ops Manager Installation.

For more information on the Ops Manager UI, see [Using the Ops Manager UI](./ops-man-ui.html).

## <a id='ops-man-api'></a> Ops Manager API

Use the Ops Manager API to configure any Ops Manager task. 

See the [Using the Ops Manager API](./ops-man-api.html) topic to learn how to get started using the [Ops Manager API](https://docs.pivotal.io/pivotalcf/2-2/opsman-api).

